    "brief": "audit/html-audit-phase-e-brief-2026-05-14.md (locked v1.1)",
    "scope": "Contract surface, dead imports, and unused features in the Vic-controlled FreeMarker templates that compose the Funnelback partial response. Reads 27 in-scope Vic-canonical templates plus 1 Squiz-platform sprite snapshot (utilities.icons.ftl). Out of scope: two Squiz-platform-core imports referenced from partial.ftl (funnelback_classic.ftl as s, funnelback.ftl as fb) which are documented as TEMPLATE_REFERENCE only; five inactive-renderer FTL files (results.video/facebook/events/twitter/instagram.ftl) which are imported by partial.ftl but whose bodies were not read per the brief's stop rules; CSS rule enumeration; FE-side consumption of the partial response (Phase B); T4 PageLayout chrome (Phase D).",
    "posture": "Read-and-record. No FTL modification. Findings categorized at recording time; rebuild design phase decides resolution. Three deliverable streams: CONTRACT_SURFACE (binding markup/seam/dispatch contracts), DEAD_IMPORT (namespace-binding-level dead imports trimmable in rebuild), UNUSED_FEATURE (macros invoked or wired but not surfaced in production output).",
