      "note_on_counts": "The brief's inventory section listed 27 Vic-canonical in-scope templates. The execution-time enumeration counted 29 because partial.ftl explicitly imports both the four active renderer files (results.news/law/programs/people.ftl) AND the five inactive renderer files (results.video/facebook/events/twitter/instagram.ftl). The five inactive renderer files are counted as in-scope in the inventory but their bodies are not read; their characterization is the one-line DEAD_IMPORT finding E28. The brief's 27 figure excludes both the active and inactive renderer files from the headline count; this audit uses 29 because the four active renderer files are characterized in full and the inactives are characterized as a one-line finding. Either count is internally consistent; the difference is bookkeeping. The 30-total-in-upload figure matches the brief."
    },
