    "brief_citation_corrections": {
      "phase_a_version_reference": "Brief v1.1 cites 'Phase A (completed 2026-05-12, v3 2026-05-13)' and references 'audit/html-audit-phase-a-2026-05-13-v3.json and .md' in Cross-references. Only 'audit/html-audit-phase-a-2026-05-12-v2.json' and '.md' are present in this repo. No v3 file exists at the cited path. This audit cites v2 throughout; the version-naming inconsistency is flagged for the brief's amendments queue or for cataloging in v17 project instructions.",
      "cta_url_list": "Brief v1.1 E.2 sub-phase decomposition lists the four hardcoded CTA URLs as '/visit, /academics/all-programs, /directory, /newsroom'. The actual hardcoded values in partial.ftl L138-158 are '/visit' (default), '/academics/all-programs' (Programs), 'https://redhawks.sharepoint.com/sites/Intranet-Home' (Faculty & Staff), '/newsroom' (News). No '/directory' value appears; the Faculty & Staff branch uses an external SharePoint URL. The count is four; one value identification was wrong. See Finding E8."
    }
