      ],
      "no_result_macro": "Despite tabs.ftl:249 calling `<@base.Result result=... view=... question=...>`, base.ftl does NOT define a Result macro. The call site is in the uninvoked Preview macro so it doesn't error at runtime; it's a latent defect \u2014 see E12.",
      "related_findings": [
