      "structural_role": "Sessions Tier 2: shortlist drawer, search history drawer, SessionCart JS init (Funnelback.SessionCart with cart-count, item templates, resultItemTrigger, cartItemTrigger config), session controls toggle (`<div class='result-sessions__controls'>` with Shortlist button aria-controls='funnelback-search-shortlist-drawer' and History button aria-controls='funnelback-search-history-drawer'), search-history link-tracker span (data-pnp-component='link-tracker' watching `.listing-item__title-link` and `.quickview__action`), shortlist Handlebars `<script id='cart-template'>` template, and per-renderer ShortlistTemplate hooks via TemplatesForResults (iterates .main namespaces for ShortlistTemplate-directives).",
      "wiring_status": "NONE OF THE TIER 2 MACROS ARE INVOKED from partial.ftl or any reached site. sessions.Controls is COMMENTED OUT at hero_banner.ftl:46. sessions.Configuration, sessions.Templates, sessions.SearchHistoryAndShortlist, sessions.ShortlistDrawer are uninvoked anywhere. The ShortlistControl self-reference at sessions.ftl:112 is inside Controls which is itself unreached.",
