    {
      "id": "unreachable-feature-templates-aggregate",
      "source_layer": "FUNNELBACK_PARTIAL",
      "source_layer_detail": "a-z_listing.ftl, extra_search.ftl, client_includes.ftl, auto_complete.ftl",
      "modifiability": {
        "who_controls": "Vic-controlled FTL"
      },
      "structural_role": "Four full templates that are imported but never invoked. a-z_listing.ftl defines BrowseModeToggle/On/Off and BrowseByFilter (gated by stencils.tabs.browse_mode.facets.<tab> profile config; carries TODO comment 'Update to suit the new design system'). extra_search.ftl defines a Preview macro (near-duplicate of tabs.Preview; both uninvoked). client_includes.ftl defines HTMLHeader/ContentHeader/ContentFooter/ClientInclude macros for CMS-injected regions (T4 PageLayout owns the page chrome, not the partial). auto_complete.ftl defines the Twitter Typeahead Configuration macro (jQuery('#query').autocompletion({...}) with datasets+templates from stencils.auto-completion.* profile config).",
